---
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro';
---

<section id="story" class="bg-secondary py-[80px]">
  <Container class="max-w-[1200px]">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[40px] font-serif font-semibold text-foreground mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-[18px] text-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Greenlawn Companies was founded by the Younkin family with a simple belief: Central Ohio families deserve access to quality, affordable homes — and the businesses that serve them should be run by people who actually live here.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[18px] text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          What started as a single manufactured home dealership on the south side of Columbus has grown into three distinct businesses, each rooted in the same values of honesty, hard work, and community.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-dark rounded-[8px] p-8 text-dark-foreground">
        <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Over four decades, the Younkin family has built and placed more than 2,000 homes across Central Ohio, operated 9 residential communities, and expanded into RV sales and specialized transport — always staying close to the customers and neighbors who made it possible.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[18px] leading-relaxed">
          Today, the second generation of the Younkin family continues to lead each business with the same hands-on approach that has defined Greenlawn from day one.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
